.TH "skb_split" 9 "skb_split" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
skb_split \- Split fragmented skb to two parts at length len.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" skb_split
.BI "(struct sk_buff *skb "  ","
.BI "struct sk_buff *skb1 "  ","
.BI "const u32 len "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "skb" 12
the buffer to split
.IP "skb1" 12
the buffer to receive the second part
.IP "len" 12
new length for skb
